ORTS ON A MEETING HELD ON THE OCCASION OF THE 50TH BIRTHDAY OF THE
TSENTRAL'NAYA NAUCHNAYA SEL'SKOKHOZYAISTVENNAYA BIBLIOTEKA VSESOYUZNOI
AKADEMII SEL'SKOKHOZYAISTVENNYKH NAUK IM. V.I. LENINA (CENTRAL AGRICULTURAL
