OF THE LIBRARY'S WORK DISCUSSED INCLUDED' METHODOLOGICAL AND BIBLIOGRAPHICAL
HELP TO PUBLIC LIBRARIES; THE LIBRARY'S COLLECTIONS AND THEIR USE; DEVELOPMENT
OF A CENTRALISED SYSTEM OF BIBLIOGRAPHIC INFORMATION IN THE FIELD OF
AGRICULTURE; THE LIBRARY'S FUNCTION AS THE METHODOLOGICAL CENTRE FOR
